nodes.text: The Force Is With Them (Mostly) is an article written by Peter Lee for the Star Wars Miniatures Clone Strike expansion set. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on May 19, 2005 and provides stats for the Force-users included in the set, such as Asajj Ventress, Darth Maul, Durge and Qui-Gon Jinn.
